quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  108,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  108,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko kousar ataa farmai hai
  108,2,to apne perwar-digaar ke liye namaz parha karo aur qurbani diya karo
  108,3,kuch shak nahi ke tumhara dushman hi be aulaad rahay ga
